race.comment: ARTPARK (4) bounced back to form in style last start at Naracoorte, putting her rivals away with ease. This isn't much tougher and a repeat of that effort has her well placed to go back-to-back. IN THE SUN (10) hasn't shown her best in her past two, but her earlier form reads strongly and she boasts an excellent record at this track. Has the speed to offset the wide draw and the claim gets her in light. A major danger. LONGWARRY (6) hasn't won for a long time but drops in grade here and draws perfectly to land in an ideal spot. His best figures make him a leading hope. LUDO (5) also appeals with the class drop and is capable of featuring.
